pubspec.description: A linter for Dart, bundled with the SDK, that helps enforce coding style, flags potentially difficult to maintain, error-prone or non-performant source and generally nudges you towards writing more idiomatic Dart. This package is vended into the SDK, where it is plugged into the analyzer framework; it is not intended to be used directly.
